arts.ttl: Stockport 1-1 Cardiff: Yousef Salech rescues Bluebirds with dramatic late equaliser
arts.sum: Cardiff City snatched a point at Edgeley Park as Yousef Salech’s 97th-minute header denied Stockport County a famous victory in League One. Nathan Trott was soon called into action, producing a superb point-blank save to deny Andresson’s header from Ben Osborn’s cross.
